  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/890b0155a058b1ce00efe43c3e50e689.poster.avif?t=1736522741\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/890b0155a058b1ce00efe43c3e50e689.webm?t=1736522741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/890b0155a058b1ce00efe43c3e50e689.mp4?t=1736522741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Help Bo wake up!</strong> Immerse yourself in a surreal lucid dream where patience and precision are required to navigate the difficult path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/62a9fc64b5981e59a96f8871e0f867bb.poster.avif?t=1736522741\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/62a9fc64b5981e59a96f8871e0f867bb.webm?t=1736522741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/62a9fc64b5981e59a96f8871e0f867bb.mp4?t=1736522741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>She is trapped in her own mind and cannot move. Only you can help her wake up by collecting the fragments and passing through the portals of awakening.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/76a496256da80b55fc06f0add42b1739.poster.avif?t=1736522741\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/76a496256da80b55fc06f0add42b1739.webm?t=1736522741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/76a496256da80b55fc06f0add42b1739.mp4?t=1736522741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>During free fall, various objects from her subconscious will interfere with your path. They are obsessively lodged in the girl’s head and create obstacles that must be overcome.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/d84f6cacb8dc133c642a0452e19a6fe6.poster.avif?t=1736522741\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/d84f6cacb8dc133c642a0452e19a6fe6.webm?t=1736522741\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2547620/extras/d84f6cacb8dc133c642a0452e19a6fe6.mp4?t=1736522741\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Original concept<br></li><li> Various obstacles and traps<br></li><li> Dreamlike atmosphere with abstract environments divided into biomes<br></li><li> Funny Ragdoll physics<br></li><li> Mini-games<br></li><li> Slow down time<br></li><li> Fast-Paced gameplay<br></li><li> Progressive difficulty<br></li><li> Great music</li></ul>",
